---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - My Blog">
  <article class="prose">
    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <p>
      Hi! I'm a frontend engineer passionate about building beautiful,
      performant web experiences. This blog is where I share my learnings,
      experiments, and thoughts about web development.
    </p>

    <h2>What I Write About</h2>

    <ul>
      <li>Web development and frontend engineering</li>
      <li>JavaScript, TypeScript, and modern frameworks</li>
      <li>Performance optimization and best practices</li>
      <li>UI/UX design principles</li>
      <li>Personal projects and experiments</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Get in Touch</h2>

    <p>
      Feel free to reach out if you'd like to connect or discuss anything
      related to web development!
    </p>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose {
    max-width: 680px;
  }

  .prose h1 {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .prose h2 {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .prose p {
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
  }

  .prose ul {
    margin: 2rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.75rem;
  }

  .prose li {
    margin-bottom: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    padding-left: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .prose li::marker {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 700;
  }
</style>
